{"tid":1856172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"CNN報導澳門再多2名賭場員工中招","createTime":"2020-02-01T13:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T13:56:57.000Z","uid":32511,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"670280678c770b1646e5d3f906195e558f919445","tid":1856172,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/asia/live-news/coronavirus-outbreak-02-01-20-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fasia%2Flive-news%2Fcoronavirus-outbreak-02-01-20-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=ANzGKs6Ysw%2B%2BKy1wioRXt4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=a1a5729f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fasia%2Flive-news%2Fcoronavirus-outbreak-02-01-20-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=b4a729b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/asia/live-news/coronavirus-outbreak-02-01-20-intl-hnk/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n兩名 starworld賭場員工染病<br />\n其中一個女性住珠海，每天&quot;通勤&quot;到澳門賭場工作，不過她是在後台工作不是接待。<br />\n另外一個男性目前沒有詳細情報<br />\n <br />\n <br />\nMacau Health Bureau is investigating the movements of two casino employees<br />\nafter it was notified by Chinese officials that they have contracted the<br />\nnovel coronavirus.<br />\n <br />\nVitor Moutinho, the bureau's spokesman, told CNN on Saturday that one of the<br />\ntwo is a woman who lives in Zhuhai in mainland China and travels to Macau<br />\ndaily for work.<br />\n <br />\nMoutinho said the woman worked at Starworld Casino in a private area, and<br />\nthat the bureau is now tracing people whom she could have come into contact<br />\nwith.<br />\n <br />\nNo further details are available about the other employee, a man.<br />\n <br />\nEmployees from the mainland who come to work in Macau have not been prevented<br />\nfrom doing so since the outbreak of the virus, and all casinos remain open<br />\nfor business."},{"pid":"7ad33906ea5f8ace0c68b6e5091f82c1a834ccae","tid":1856172,"uid